hpnicfMultilinkPPP.name: hpnicfMultilinkPPP
hpnicfMultilinkPPP.description: The HPN-ICF-MP-MIB provides read access to MP(Multilink PPP) link status information. The information available through this MIB includes: the father channel, the bundled son channel, the slot on which MP bundled, the number of son channels, the bundle name, the statistic of lost fragments, reordered packets, unassigned packets, interleaved packets, and the received/sent sequence, etc.

hpnicfMpMultilinkTable.name: hpnicfMpMultilinkTable
hpnicfMpMultilinkTable.description: This table describes the information of MP link. The index of this table is the interface index of MP group or VT(Virtual Template).

hpnicfMpMultilinkEntry.name: hpnicfMpMultilinkEntry
hpnicfMpMultilinkEntry.description: Each entry in this table describes the information of MP link. The available information includes: the father channel, the slot on which MP bundled, the number of bundled son channels, the statistics of lost fragments, reordered packets, unassigned packets, interleaved packets, and received/sent sequence.

hpnicfMpMultilinkDescr.name: hpnicfMpMultilinkDescr
hpnicfMpMultilinkDescr.description: The interface name of the father interface on which MP bundled. It is the name of a Virtual Temblate or a MP group.

hpnicfMpBundleName.name: hpnicfMpBundleName
hpnicfMpBundleName.description: The bundle name of the multilink. when authentication is configured, the bundle name is the authenticated user name; when authentication not configured, the bundle name is multilink.

hpnicfMpBundledSlot.name: hpnicfMpBundledSlot
hpnicfMpBundledSlot.description: The slot on which MP bundled.

hpnicfMpBundledMemberCnt.name: hpnicfMpBundledMemberCnt
hpnicfMpBundledMemberCnt.description: The number of the bundled son channel of the MP link.

hpnicfMpLostFragments.name: hpnicfMpLostFragments
hpnicfMpLostFragments.description: The number of fragments of the MP link discarded because bad fragments received, or assembling packet failed, etc.

hpnicfMpReorderedPkts.name: hpnicfMpReorderedPkts
hpnicfMpReorderedPkts.description: The number of received packets of the MP link reordered.

hpnicfMpUnassignedPkts.name: hpnicfMpUnassignedPkts
hpnicfMpUnassignedPkts.description: The number of received packets of the MP link waiting for reordering.

hpnicfMpInterleavedPkts.name: hpnicfMpInterleavedPkts
hpnicfMpInterleavedPkts.description: The number of received packets of the MP link interleaved by the packets queued in RTPQ(Real-time Transport Protocol Queue) or LLQ(Low Latency Queue).

hpnicfMpRcvdSequence.name: hpnicfMpRcvdSequence
hpnicfMpRcvdSequence.description: The current sequence number of the MP link for receiving.

hpnicfMpSentSequence.name: hpnicfMpSentSequence
hpnicfMpSentSequence.description: The current sequence number of the MP link for sending.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkTable.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkTable
hpnicfMpMemberlinkTable.description: This table describes the information of son channels of the MP link. The index of this table is the interface index of MP group or VT(Virtual Template).

hpnicfMpMemberlinkEntry.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkEntry
hpnicfMpMemberlinkEntry.description: Each entry in this table describes the information of the bundled son channels of MP link. The available information includes: the interface index of the son channel, the interface name of the son channel.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkSeqNumber.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkSeqNumber
hpnicfMpMemberlinkSeqNumber.description: The bundled sequence number of the son channels of the MP link. This object is one of the index of the table.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkIfIndex.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkIfIndex
hpnicfMpMemberlinkIfIndex.description: The interface index of the son channels of the MP link.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkDescr.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkDescr
hpnicfMpMemberlinkDescr.description: The interface name of the son channels of the MP link.

hpnicfMpMemberlinkMpStatus.name: hpnicfMpMemberlinkMpStatus
hpnicfMpMemberlinkMpStatus.description: The MP status of the son channels of the MP link.

hpnicfMpCompliance.name: hpnicfMpCompliance
hpnicfMpCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the Multilink PPP MIB.

hpnicfMpMandatoryGroup.name: hpnicfMpMandatoryGroup
hpnicfMpMandatoryGroup.description: A collection of objects providing mandatory MP information.

hpnicfMpInfoGroup.name: hpnicfMpInfoGroup
hpnicfMpInfoGroup.description: All running information of MP feature.
